 text-decoration: underline;">according to the WHO</a>, about 100 million p=
eople are pushed into extreme poverty because of healthcare costs worldwide=
, and insurers struggle to find a business model that works.&nbsp;</p><p st=
yle=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em =
0;">The problem is so large as to seem intractable.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"co=
lor: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">Then =
